        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the rice is cooking, chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely (save a few leaves for garnish!)</p><p>Combine <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped basil </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) with the <strong>crème fraîche </strong>– this is your<strong> basil crème fraîche</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
