    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Chop the <strong>drained mozzarella</strong> into small cubes</p><p>Combine the <strong>cubed mozzarella</strong> with your <strong>sun-dried tomato paste</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>basil</strong>, a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your<strong> basil mozzarella</strong></p>",
