        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat them dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Once the risotto is ready, stir through the <strong>roasted tomatoes</strong> and <strong>remaining grated Italian hard cheese </strong>– this is your <strong>roasted tomato risotto</strong></p><p>Top the <strong>ciabatta crostinis</strong> with the <strong>basil mozzarella</strong> – these are your <strong>mozzarella crostinis</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
