    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>roasted tomato risotto </strong>topped<strong> </strong>with the<strong> basil crème fraîche</strong>, a<strong> heart crisp</strong>, the <strong>reserved basil leaves</strong> and the <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>mozzarella crostinis </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
